\bigl(1-e^{-k_{p}t}\bigr)\Bigr]\;
\frac{\dot N_{\text{gen}}}{\lambda}\,k_{\text{assoc}}^{\max}\theta_{\infty}
\Bigg[
\frac{e^{\beta t}-1}{\beta}
-\frac{e^{(\beta-k_{p})t}-1}{\beta-k_{p}}
-\frac{e^{(\beta-\lambda)t}-1}{\beta-\lambda}
